# Safety net: the wildcard extension patterns above (*.png, *.jpg, etc.) are
# meant to exclude the legacy scraped-site image dumps, but being unanchored
# they also match real app source assets like apps/web/app/icon.png. Never
# let them exclude anything under the actual Next.js app.
!www.lawsonstate.edu/apps/web/**
